title: A discussion of the relationship between the US and Russia
itunes:title: A discussion of the relationship between the US and Russia
description:
George and Joseph Weisberg discuss Putin's influence in Russia. They also touch on improving US and Russia relations, Russia pulling out of NATO and what Putin wants for the future of Russia vs what the people of Russia want for the future of Russia.
